caption:
@wasiindia in search of young Humpback Mahseer. With more young recruits, lies hope for survival of the species which have been declared Critically Endangered. Here's hoping the little ones grow up to be the giants that once roamed the Cauvery in abundance. 

Reposted via @wasiindia

